POST /tasks/:taskId/comments
1. Authenticate user
2. Validate taskId
3. Validate request body
4. Find task
5. Check task exists
6. Check user has access
7. Create comment
8. Set:
   - taskId
   - userId = current user
9. Create ActivityLog
10. Return comment

DELETE comments/: commentId
1. Authenticate user
2. Validate commentId
3. Find comment
4. Check comment exists
5. Find task
6. Find project
7. Check workspace role
8. Verify:
   - user is comment author
   OR
   - user is OWNER/ADMIN
9. Delete comment
10. Create ActivityLog
11. Return success

PATCH /comments/:commentId
1. Authenticate user
2. Validate commentId
3. Validate request body
4. Find comment
5. Check comment exists
6. Verify current user is comment author
7. Update content
8. Update updatedAt
9. Create ActivityLog
10. Return updated comment

